classes.name: ServiceDependency
classes.note: Collects all dependencies of a software module or component on an AUTOSAR Service related to a specific item (e.g. an NVRAM Block, a diagnostic event etc.). It defines the quality of service (Service Needs) of this item as well as (optionally) references to additional elements. This information is required for tools in order to generate the related basic software configuration and ServiceSwComponentTypes.
